I '''Susan Abigail Sarandon''' (mibait a Tomalin; mibait Octubre 4, 1946)<ref>{{cite news|last=Bernice|first=Janet|title=Susan Catches Wales|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=TzgEAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA39&dq=susan%20Tomalin&pg=PA39#v=onepage&q=susan%20Tomalin&f=false|accessdate=March 27, 2011|newspaper=Ancestry Magazine|date=March/April 2007}}</ref> metung yang Americanang artista. Megobra ne kareng pelikula ampong telebisyon manibat 1969, at sinambut yang [[Academy Award for Best Actress]] para king lage na king pelikulang ''[[Dead Man Walking (pelikula)|Dead Man Walking]]'' anyang 1995. Menikwa ne muring nominasyun para king gagal para kareng apat a pelikula bayu ita at mekatanggap neng aliwa pang pamangilala king kayang obra. Pikabaluan ya king kayang aktibismung pangketawan o sosyal ampong pampulitika kareng miyayaliwang sangkan a liberal. [[Renmar Arnejo]]

